name: AmiyaRestaurant
0:
”Alexa, ask amiya restaurant what is the deal of the day”
”Alexa, ask amiya restaurant find me some coupons”
”Alexa, ask amiya restaurant give me guidance”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: amiya restaurant
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Search Amiya Restaurant product catalog and ask for any coupons or deals. For example you can
- ask "amiya restaurant what is the deal of the day" or 
- ask "amiya restaurant find me some coupon" or
- ask "amiya restaurant for any deals" or 
- ask "amiya restaurant for any coupons"
- ask "for help"
